resources.string: I am a good guy.Soon I will be a good programmer. It is my goal. I will not give up - that is for sure! Come on, I see the goal ... The path will lead to the right stage - that is for sure. It is necessary to push and run. We will reach, crawl and reach.I would have much more time to tell and it would be necessary ... I will wait and think, and then I will write. My goals do not change. They will alternately be left behind. And success will be obvious. Joy is worthy.
